ml.alternet.security.auth.hashers.impl

Class MD5BasedHasher

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.alternet.security.auth.hashers.impl.HasherBase<SaltedParts>
      • ml.alternet.security.auth.hashers.impl.MD5BasedHasher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ml.alternet.security.auth.Credentials.Checker, Hasher

    public class MD5BasedHasher
extends HasherBase<SaltedParts>
    The MD5 based BSD password algorithm 1 and apr1 (Apache variant). Usually in the Modular Crypt Format :
    1. Apache MD5 crypt format :
      $apr1$jgwedrkq$jzeetEHMGal5H0SUFDMEl1
    2. Crypt MD5 :
      $1$3iuE5z/b$JHyXMzQOIq3cl6WlEMoZC.
    Author:
    Philippe Poulard
